text: This was the first edition of the tournament. Illya Marchenko and Denys Molchanov won the title, defeating Roman Jebavý and Błażej Koniusz in the final, 7–6(7–4), 6–3. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Main Draw Trofeo Citta di Brescia - Doubles Category:Trofeo Città di Brescia
